Package: rtop
Type: Package
Title: Interpolation of data with variable spatial support
Version: 0.3-38
Date: 2013-04-22
Author: Jon Olav Skoien
Maintainer: Jon Olav Skoien <jon.skoien@gmail.com>
Depends: sp, gstat
Suggests: igraph, rgdal, intamap
Description: Package for geostatistical interpolation of data with irregular spatial support, such as runoff related data or some types of data from administrative units.
License: GPL (>= 2)
